Package com.mycompany.anothercam

Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
com.mycompany.anothercam.Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
The public Enumeration of the visibility status of the camp. PENDING: Enquriries are pending and yet to be replied by staff/student committee PROCESSED: Enquiries are processed and replied by staff/student committee
